description:
Sarah Ketterer, CEO of the $50 billion long-only equity value shop Causeway Capital Management, sits down with David Rubenstein to discuss her approach to value investing, running a 100-person firm, and why she sees the biggest opportunities ahead in international markets. This interview was filmed July 9 in New York.
